These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, june, april, september
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama, superhero
4 different games are played: domino, poker, monopoly, canasta
House: cottage, gothic-revival, craftsman, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise, lilac, light-blue
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person playing canasta is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who likes light-blue##2
 3. the cottage house is the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person playing monopoly##2
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Birthday           | april | july   | september | june |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | disaster | drama              | superhero |
| Game   | domino       | poker     | canasta               | monopoly    |
| House           | gothic-revival        | craftsman     | art-deco           | cottage       |
| Color     | turquise | lilac     | mauve                | light-blue      |

