.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, july, october
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports, epic
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, pink, ivory
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, quad-bike, van
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person driving the bus##2
 4. the person who likes ivory is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday          | july       | april      | august      | october      |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | musical | sports | horror |
| Color   | ivory          | light-blue       | pink            | blood-red      |
| Transport           | airplane            | quad-bike    | bus           | van       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

