.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, banana, grapefruit, strawberry
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, azalea, bellflower, orchid
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, writing, baking
City: liverpool, colone, paris, san-francisco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, june, september
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is between the person who growsazalea and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | asparagus  | strawberry | grapefruit |
| Flower   | daffodil   | bellflower        | azalea | orchid     |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks    | baking  | writing   |
| City           | paris     | san-francisco      | liverpool | colone        |
| Birthday         | november      | september | march      | june     |

