.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
House: tower, cottage, victorian, townhouse
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, pomegranate, spinach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, bellflowerpy, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, may, june
4 different pets are kept: pony, hamster, turtle, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person eating avocado##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growstulip##2
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the victorian house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who growstulip is between the person who's birthday is in february and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsbellflowerpy##1
 8. the tower house is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the cottage house is between the owner of the hamster and the person who growsbellflowerpy##2
10. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
11. the person eating corn is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| House      | townhouse     | cottage | victorian    | tower          |
| Food          | spinach | avocado     | pomegranate | corn         |
| Flower   | bellflowerpy    | tulip       | bellflower         | azalea        |
| Birthday         | june  | december     | february     | may |
| Pet     | pony     | turtle      | hamster   | hedgehog          |

