 2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the german##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the ship and the person drinking lemonade##2
11. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |      4       |
