 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 3. the dressmaker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is the dressmaker##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is the dancer##1
 8. the musician is between the dressmaker and the person playing billiard##2
 9. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person playing billiard and the person traveling to berlin##2
11. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Game          | billiard       | scrabble       | backgammon | poker    |
| City         | london     | liverpool | berlin | prague     |
